title: Buying or Selling on the Red-Hot Chargers and Waiver Wire Must-Adds After Week 6 | The Dantasy Football Podcast (Ep. 323)
description:
The Ringer’s Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly offer their initial advice after Week 6 (1:45), break down the must-add players off of waivers for the upcoming week (18:00), and discuss which players on the red-hot Chargers are worth buying low or selling high (26:30).
